products.title: Unilux PVC Blackout Flamingo Pink Roller Blind
products.metadescription: Unilux PVC Blackout Flamingo Pink Roller Blind in Pink. Made to measure from £10.04 with FREE UK mainland delivery. This Roller Blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription:
Embrace fantastic flamingo pink & give your bathroom or kitchen a modern makeover with the Unilux PVC Blackout Roller Blind. This roller blind is made from moisture resistant PVC and is guaranteed to give your space a fresh feel thanks to its contemporary design and crisp white finish. In addition, the blackout material will provide the required peace and privacy.
 
 Product ID: SDB-RBX2380 Fabric Colour: Flamingo Pink Material: Fiberglass core laminated with PVC layered coating Lining: Colour Match Backing - See Sample Headrail: Durable Aluminium Roller Tube Supported By White Steel Brackets - Top, Face or Side Fix     Control Type: Smooth Continuous-Looped Chain Energy Saving Rating: ER3 - Highest Energy Saving Value - UV Protection and Effective Thermal Retention Blackout: Yes
